  "commentary": "With SPX at 7020.54 sitting between the max negative gamma at 7015 and max positive gamma at 7050, dealers are likely buying this dip to hedge their long gamma positions, providing natural support. The PIN regime with massive positive GEX walls at 7000 (+9720.9M) and 7050 (+9994.1M) creates a powerful stabilizing force that should limit downside and cap any bounce attempts. Watch 7015 as the key inflection point - breaks below trigger more dealer buying while moves toward 7050 face heavy selling pressure from dealer hedging.\n\nBottom line: expect price to grind sideways between 7000-7050 with limited breakout potential.",
